# Cookieless analytics via Umami (https://umami.is). Leave unset to disable
# analytics entirely (no script loads, no consent banner needed).
# Get the website id from your Umami dashboard.
VITE_UMAMI_WEBSITE_ID=
# Optional: script URL. Defaults to Umami Cloud if omitted.
# VITE_UMAMI_SRC=https://cloud.umami.is/script.js
